  "body": "- [X] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\nWhen using Truffle Debugger to debug a contract call rejection without source maps available, the debugger does not show you the rejection message.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\nDebug a contract without source maps.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\nSee the rejection message even if source maps are unavailable for the transaction being debugged.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\nJust a \"reject\" with no message.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Windows 10\r\n* Ethereum client: Ganache\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.0.x\r\n* node version (`node --version`): v12.3.0\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 6.9.0\r\n",
